item.title: Wich server is the best?
item.dc:creator: @Team_Rocket Team_Rocket
item.description:
@Team_Rocket wrote:

asshole_rule:

What Rocket said, they will seem really hard at first, but it’s better to learn with a good base(like those he stated) then to start out with something shitty like PI or Delta.

For once we are in agreement about something, I salute you for not starting an argument with me. I’m proud of myself for not starting one as well.

I’m willing to call off this little debate if you are. I’m mature enough to apologize, are you? If so, then we should both just apologize and move on, arguing is accomplishing nothing when we could both be contributing to the community. Then again, doing that in the Server Help section is contributing (lol).
